The Peano map is a function from the unit interval to the unit square.
-/
def peano_map (x : Set.Icc (0 : ℝ) 1) : Set.Icc (0 : ℝ) 1 × Set.Icc (0 : ℝ) 1 :=
  let (u, v) := cantor_extension x
  (retraction_Icc u, retraction_Icc v)

/-
The scaled Peano map transforms the unit interval to a larger square.
-/
